content.text: Andy: Did I do this for me? No, I did this for the little guy. For Joe Sixpack. The guy who wakes up every morning in his four hundred dollar a month apartment, wonders how's he gonna pay his mortgage that month. Wonders how he's gonna fill his car up with oil. Wonders how he's gonna pay his kid's orphanage bills. That guy shouldn't have to wonder where he's gonna park.
